 {"id":"bd-1vr1.3","title":"Build real DB + service test harness","description":"Create a shared test harness that boots the gateway with a real sqlite DB (temp path per test run), runs migrations, and exposes helpers for seeding accounts/agents/alerts/etc. Ensure WAL + cleanup are deterministic. Provide utilities to spin up/tear down the Bun server and WebSocket hub for integration tests. Success: tests can run against real services without mocks.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:26:30.022568928Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-29T04:30:25.509225586Z","closed_at":"2026-01-29T04:30:25.509157229Z","close_reason":"Built gateway-harness.ts in packages/test-utils with: temp SQLite DB per test run, automatic migration runner, seed/cleanup/exec helpers, server boot support, WAL pragmas. All 8 tests pass.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1vr1.3","depends_on_id":"bd-1vr1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
 {"id":"bd-1vr1.4","title":"Deterministic runtime controls for tests","description":"Standardize time/UUID/random controls so tests can assert exact outputs without mocks. Provide utilities for fixed timestamps, seeded randomness, and deterministic IDs where needed (ideally via config injection, not mock.module). Success: flaky timing eliminated and integration tests can rely on reproducible state.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:26:41.481131212Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-29T04:32:22.559109899Z","closed_at":"2026-01-29T04:32:22.559043956Z","close_reason":"Added deterministic.ts with createIdGenerator, installDeterministicIds (crypto.randomUUID replacement), createSeededRandom (xoshiro128**), installSeededRandom (Math.random replacement). All 9 tests pass.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1vr1.4","depends_on_id":"bd-1vr1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
 {"id":"bd-1vr1.5","title":"Playwright logging + diagnostics framework","description":"Add a shared E2E logging framework: capture browser console/error events, network request/response summaries, WebSocket messages, and timing metrics; enable trace/video/screenshot artifacts on failure; and emit a structured run log per test. Update Playwright config/reporters accordingly. Success: every E2E test yields a deterministic log bundle usable for debugging.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:26:52.579658560Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T21:38:11.568343040Z","closed_at":"2026-01-27T21:38:11.568323112Z","close_reason":"Implementation complete - E2E logging framework with TestLogger, fixtures, StructuredReporter, and updated Playwright config. Captures console/network/WebSocket/timing. Duplicate files (e2e-reporter.ts, test-fixture.ts) can be cleaned up.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1vr1.5","depends_on_id":"bd-1vr1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-29T04:21:46Z","created_by":"import"}]}
