 {"id":"bd-2n73","title":"Gateway + private sync with ACFS/tooling vNext","description":"Objective: align Flywheel Gateway (public) and flywheel_private (private) with the latest ACFS manifest v2 and the expanded Dicklesworthstone tool ecosystem. Incorporate new tools/utilities, updated robot/JSON/TOON interfaces, and ACFS manifest-driven metadata so the dashboard, APIs, and detection logic match the real installed stack. Constraints: keep business-sensitive configs in /dp/flywheel_private; avoid leaking private data into public repo. Success: Gateway presents accurate tool inventory/health, supports new tool APIs, and private repo holds sensitive configs/overrides.","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:05.828388561Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-27T18:37:05.828388561Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
